node.text:
This is our last Christmas in this house. We’ve lived here over 14 years. The memories we’ve created will live in our hearts forever! Christmas has been especially magical here. I wanted to share our house one last time all decked out for Christmas! Enjoy!
Xo

- all the sources for our Christmas Home Tour can be found on my website.

- #christmastour #christmashometour #christmasdecor #christmasstyle

node.text:
Here’s a little tour of our family room decked out for Christmas! To see the full home tour, visit my latest blog post. I have all the sources there for you too. 
I hope you enjoy it! If you do, I’ll share each room. Let me know!
Xo💗
-
-
-
-
-#christmashometour #christmasdecor #christmasfamilyroom #flockedchristmastree  #christmasmantel

node.text:
The Wren is really coming to life! Swipe left to see a peek at some of the details added over the past few weeks! Can you believe how quickly it’s coming together?! 
My world feels like it is spinning a thousand miles an hour with the build, the book launch (in a few weeks - visit my stories for more details), a new website, back to school and life! How are you guys holding up?!
Xo💗
-
-
-
-
#thewren #dreamhome #newbuild #frenchhome #traditionalhome

node.text:
I just added a fun new blog post to my website sourcing my entire kitchen for less as part of @wayfair ‘s Save Big, Give Big sale! They are giving 10% of the sale proceeds to the charity Built from Zero to help end homelessness. You can save up to 80%, while giving back and helping someone build the home they dreamed of. 
Head to my blog for all the sources or visit the like to know it app where I have items sourced for you.
Xo💗

-

node.text:
Trips to Coronado have been a family tradition since I was a little girl. It’s a magical place with the most gorgeous sunsets! Matt and I honeymooned here at the Hotel Del and have enjoyed bringing our kids to the same golden sand beaches we stuck our toes in as children. I loved looking around seeing families playing together and enjoying being together. It’s what life is all about. 
Gosh, I don’t want summer to end!!!
Xo💗

node.text:
Who loves ginger jars?!!! Swipe left to see some simple Summer styling tips with lots of my favorite ginger jars, faux florals and accessories l, all from @wayfair! They have some really beautiful jars that are hard to find. These are ones I love to add to my collection. Unique, special jars that you’ll love for a lifetime. Head to my blog to see my tips for starting your own collection and of course for all the sources. 
Xo💙
